text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to apply for a marriage certificate in dwarka?
text.Response A: The marriage registration office in dwarka is located at plot no. 3, Sector-14, near the district courts. You have to first fill up the marriage registration form, and the marriage registrar will guide you through the rest of the process.
text.Response B: Sure! To apply for a marriage certificate in Delhi, you will need to go to the office of the registering officer in your area. The registering officer is responsible for issuing marriage certificates in Delhi.
